9.description: Made without Gluten-Containing Ingredients: Due to our open kitchens that handle gluten, we cannot guarantee that items made without gluten-containing ingredients are “gluten-free,” as defined by the FDA. We encourage guests to speak to the chef or manager regarding any questions about ingredients.
